					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Ettvard Needle is the editor of the Baldur's Mouth Gazette. He is proudly pro-Gortash, obnoxious towards the PC, and insinuates (wel, directly states at the moment)  that the gazette is about to print a hit piece about the players.\r\n\r\nPlayers can intimidate Ettvard for some info, or use blackmail on him if they have found it to keep the hit piece from being published."
				}
